[5] «{'snippet': 'Krantivira Sangolli Rayanna Railway Station (formerly known as City Railway Station) is an underground metro station on the East-West corridor of the Purple Line of Namma Metro which serves the Subhash Nagar area, Sevashrama area in Bangalore, India.', 'title': 'Krantivira Sangolli Rayanna Railway Station metro station', 'link': 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Krantivira_Sangolli_Rayanna_Railway_Station_metro_station'}»",
  "Question": "What is the name of bangalore city railway station?",
  "Disambiguations": "DQ 1: What is the official name of Bangalore City Railway Station?;
DA 1: Krantivira Sangolli Rayanna Bengaluru Station
DQ 2: What is the common abbreviation for Bangalore City Railway Station?;
