DA 4: KSR",
  "Answer": "Bangalore City Railway Station has several names. Officially, it is known as Krantivira Sangolli Rayanna Bengaluru Station. It is commonly referred to as KSR Bengaluru Station, with the most common abbreviation being KSR. The station was formerly known as City Railway Station."
